---
title: Blog
description: The landing page for the blog.
layout: page.njk
---

<div class="text-center m-8">
    <span class="text-8xl font-bubble text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-pink-400 hover:from-pink-400 hover:to-blue-400">
        Blog
    </span>
</div>
<br>

<div class="flex justify-center w-full">
    <div class="flex-col text-center max-w-prose">
        <p class="px-5 text-lg text-center dark:text-white">
            Welcome to my blog! It's currently organized into three categories,
            possibly with more coming in future. They're listed below. Hopefully
            you find something you like in here!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
<p class="px-5 text-5xl font-bubble dark:text-white">Pinned Posts</p>
<div class="flex justify-center w-full">
    <ul class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center justify-items-center">
    {% for post in collections._pinned %}
        <li class="px-5">
            <div class="text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 mt-8 p-8 max-w-xs" onclick="window.location.href = '{{ post.url }}'">
                <p class="text-4xl font-bubble dark:text-white">{{ post.data.title }}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    {{
                        post
                            .date
                            .toLocaleDateString()
                    }}
                </p>
            </div>
        </li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>
<br><br>
<p class="px-5 text-5xl font-bubble dark:text-white">Latest Posts</p>
<div class="flex justify-center w-full">
    <ul class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center justify-items-center">
    {% for post in collections._blog %}
        <li class="px-5">
            <div class="text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 mt-8 p-8 max-w-xs" onclick="window.location.href = '{{ post.url }}'">
                <p class="text-4xl font-bubble dark:text-white">{{ post.data.title }}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">
                    {{
                        post
                            .date
                            .toLocaleDateString()
                    }}
                </p>
            </div>
        </li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>
<br><br>
<p class="text-5xl font-bubble dark:text-white">Categories</p>
<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 justify-center justify-items-center">
    {% set items = [
        {
            name: "Dev",
            description: "All things development. Programming, computer science, web design, etc.",
            gradientClasses: "bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-indigo-500 hover:from-indigo-500 hover:to-green-500"
        },
        {
            name: "Prod",
            description: "Productivity and my journey to becoming a better version of myself.",
            gradientClasses: "bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-yellow-500 hover:from-yellow-500 hover:to-pink-500"
        },
        {
            name: "Σοφος",
            description: "Anything and everything I find intellectually stimulating, from philosophy to physics.",
            gradientClasses: "bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-purple-500 hover:from-purple-500 hover:to-red-500"
        }
    ] %}
    {% for item in items %}
    <li class="px-5">
        <div class="text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 mt-8 p-8 max-w-xs {{ item.gradientClasses }}" onclick="window.location.href = '/blog/dev'">
            <p class="text-4xl text-white font-bubble">{{ item.name }}</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">{{ item.description }}</p>
        </div>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
</ul>
